<p><b>“Good Talk, Dad” Sweepstakes</b></p>
<p><b>OFFICIAL RULES</b></p>
<p><b>NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. A PURCHASE WILL NOT IMPROVE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING.</b></p>
<p><strong>Eligibility:</strong><b> </b>The<b> </b><b>“Good Talk, Dad” Sweepstakes </b>(the “Sweepstakes”) is open to legal residents of the 48 contiguous United States and the District of Columbia (U.S.), age 18 or older at time of entry. Void in AK, HI, U.S. Territories and Possessions, Puerto Rico, outside the U.S. and wherever else prohibited by law. Employees of The Michael J. Fox Foundation for Parkinson’s Research (the "Sponsor"), its subsidiaries, affiliates, their participating advertising and promotion agencies, and the immediate family members of, and/or those living in the same household of each, are not eligible to enter. Sweepstakes is subject to all applicable federal, state and local laws and regulations.</p>
<p><strong>Entry:</strong> Visit <a href="http://www.facebook.com/michaeljfoxfoundation">www.facebook.com/michaeljfoxfoundation</a>, click "Good Talk, Dad” Sweeps tab, click “Like” to become a fan of The Michael J. Fox Foundation<b> </b>Facebook page <strong>and</strong> follow all entry instructions to complete and submit the online entry form. <strong>Online entries must be received</strong><b> </b><b>between Monday, July 7, 2014 at 12:01 PM Eastern Time (“ET”) and Sunday, August 3, 2014 at 11:59 PM ET, <strong>(the "Sweepstakes Entry Period").</strong></b> Online entrants are subject to all notices posted online including but not limited to the Sponsor’s Privacy Policy. <b>Limit one (1) online entry per person or email address regardless if entrant has more than one (1) email address.</b> In the event of a dispute, online entries will be deemed to have been submitted by the Authorized Account Holder of the email address submitted at the time of entry. "Authorized Account Holder" means the natural person who is assigned to an email address by an Internet access provider, online service provider, or other organization that is responsible for assigning email addresses for the domain associated with the submitted email address.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><b>Prize/Approximate Retail Value (“ARV”): </b>Two (2) potential Grand Prize winners will be awarded one copy of Good Talk, Dad signed by Bill and Willie Geist. Total ARV of Grand Prize: $27.00. </p>
<p><strong>Random Drawings:</strong> The winners will be selected in a random drawing taking place on or about <b>Monday, <strong>August 4, 2014</strong> </b>from among all eligible entries received, <strong>which will take place</strong> at the offices of The Michael J. Fox Foundation for Parkinson’s Research.</p>
<p><strong>Grand Prize winner will be notified by email and confirmed in writing. Prize package will be awarded within approximately Forty-five (45) days after the winner is verified. </strong><b> </b><b> </b></p>
<p><b>Odds</b>: The odds of winning are dependent upon the number of eligible entries received.</p>
<p><b>Prize Conditions: </b> If prize notification is returned as undeliverable, if winner is found ineligible, if winner cannot accept or receive the prize for any reason within the time frame specified, or he/she is not in compliance with these Official Rules, the corresponding prize will be forfeited and an alternate winner may be selected in a separate random drawing.</p>
